snippet.title: Worker 42 - Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Worker 42 is a single-player first-person exploration game. Use your scanner to find your way in the interstellar darkness of space. Repair the various systems of the station, complete your tasks and return to Earth. But something seems wrong on this planet.

Whislist on Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/3169590/Worker_42/
